Module: jinja2\_.py
-------------------

The Module ``jinja2_.py`` contains the static class ``Jinja2``

Class: Jinja2
^^^^^^^^^^^^^

The static Class ``Jinja2`` provides I/O Control methods for Jinja2 files;
it contains the subsequent methods.

